## Error Reference

| Situation | Action |
|---|---|
| Sta.sh download fails | Stop entire workflow — do not attempt any uploads |
| 500px upload fails | Log error, continue to 35photo |
| 35photo upload fails | Log error, continue to Facebook |
| Facebook CAPTCHA | Pause and ask user to solve manually |
| Facebook post fails | Log error, continue to DA |
| DA API fails | Log error — this is the most critical failure since Sta.sh item may already be consumed. Tell user the DA URL was not created. |
| File picker can't find temp file | Check if Google Drive has synced. Wait 30 seconds and retry. |
| `requests` not installed | Run `pip install requests` in the VM terminal |

